---
import MiFoto from "../../assets/img/MiFoto.png";
---

<!-- Contenedor principal -->
<div
  class="mx-auto mt-20 flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-8 px-6 lg:flex-row"
>
  <!-- Imagen -->
  <div
    class="border-primary h-64 w-64 overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-lg md:h-96 md:w-96 drop-shadow-[4px_4px_0_#7836cf]"
  >
    <img
      src={MiFoto.src}
      alt="Foto de Cristian Dev"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Texto -->
  <div class="flex-1 text-center text-gray-300 lg:text-left">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">
      My name is <span class="text-white text-shadow">Cristian</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4">
      I am a frontend developer that builds responsive and interactive web
      applications focused on <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >front-end development</span
      > and the
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">user experience</span>,
      participating in both frontend and backend development, integrating
      interfaces, business logic, APIs and databases according to each project's
      needs. I work with technologies such as React, Node.js, Astro, JavaScript,
      TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, SASS and design tools like Figma.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      I specialize in transforming <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >UI designs</span
      > into functional interfaces, building dynamic and modular
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">components</span>, and
      structuring clean, maintainable, and scalable frontend code.
      I have built multiple real-world projects published on <span
        class="text-primary font-semibold">GitHub</span
      > tuve mi primer contacto con el mundo de la programación. Motivado por la
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">curiosidad</span>, continué
      estudiando, y decidí que esto era a lo que quería dedicarme a nivel <span
        class="text-primary font-semibold">profesional</span
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2">
      Siempre estoy comprometido con un <span class="text-primary font-semibold"
        >constante crecimiento</span
      > y
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">mejora</span> en mis habilidades, buscando
      adaptarme a los nuevos
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">avances tecnológicos</span> y superarme
      a nivel
      <span class="text-primary font-semibold">profesional</span> y <span
        class="text-primary font-semibold">personal</span
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
